<%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <!-- About Us Section -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-blue-200 mt-20 py-16">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-blue-800 mb-8">About Us</h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                Luminous International School is dedicated to providing a nurturing and dynamic learning environment for
                all students. Our mission is to foster academic excellence, personal growth, and character development.
                We believe in empowering our students to become responsible, thoughtful, and compassionate individuals
                who will thrive in a rapidly changing world. With a strong commitment to innovation, we integrate modern
                educational tools and teaching methods to support our students in achieving their fullest potential. At
                Luminous, we aim to build a community of respect, integrity, and lifelong learning.
            </p>


            <!-- Mission, Vision, Values Section -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-16">
                <!-- Mission -->
                <div
                    class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg transform transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-xl duration-300 ease-in-out">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-6">Our Mission</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                        To empower educational institutions by providing a seamless, user-friendly platform that manages
                        administrative tasks, enhances communication, and supports learning outcomes.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Vision -->
                <div
                    class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg transform transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-xl duration-300 ease-in-out">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-6">Our Vision</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                        To become the leading educational technology platform, transforming schools worldwide into
                        more organized, communicative, and effective environments for students and staff alike.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Values -->
                <div
                    class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg transform transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-xl duration-300 ease-in-out">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-6">Our Values</h3>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                        <li>Innovation: Continuously improving and adapting to meet educational needs.</li>
                        <li>Integrity: Building trust through transparency and ethical practices.</li>
                        <li>Collaboration: Fostering partnerships to improve the learning environment.</li>
                        <li>Excellence: Striving for the highest standards in everything we do.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Our Story Section -->
            <div class="mt-16">
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-blue-800 text-center mb-8">Our Story</h3>
                <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                        SchoolSystem was founded by a team of educators and technology enthusiasts with a shared vision:
                        to simplify the way schools operate and improve the overall educational experience. We
                        recognized
                        the need for a comprehensive solution to manage administrative processes, academic records,
                        staff
                        communication, and student engagement in a single, intuitive platform.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                        With years of experience in the education sector, we set out to create a platform that could
                        bring
                        all aspects of school management under one roof. Today, SchoolSystem serves educational
                        institutions
                        worldwide, helping them enhance efficiency, improve collaboration, and provide better
                        experiences
                        for both staff and students.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Call to Action Section -->
            <div class="mt-16 text-center">
                <a href="/contact"
                    class="inline-block bg-blue-800 text-white text-lg font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 ease-in-out">
                    Get in Touch
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

